author: audit-docs-tests-agent
acceptance_criteria: "- An integration test exercises the full close-many flow: create items, close-many with reason, capture checkpoint-id, rollback, verify items restored to pre-close state\n- Test uses sandbox PM_PATH (node scripts/run-tests.mjs pattern)"
parent: pm-u9d0
risk: low
confidence: high
resolution: "Integration test creates items, close-many --filter-tag --reason (matched/closed=2, checkpoint id captured), verifies closed, close-many --rollback <id> (restored=2), verifies items reopened with close_reason cleared, and an out-of-filter item untouched."
expected_result: close-many rollback restore path exercised end-to-end with sandbox PM_PATH.
actual_result: 1 integration test; apply + rollback output shapes asserted; passes.
